1
00:01:00,960 --> 00:01:01,439
Imperial Uncle.

2
00:01:01,439 --> 00:01:01,840
Here.

3
00:01:11,959 --> 00:01:12,359
Hey.

4
00:01:13,519 --> 00:01:14,319
What are you thinking about?

5
00:01:14,799 --> 00:01:15,760
Oh, nothing.

6
00:01:17,280 --> 00:01:18,079
Hey, everyone.

7
00:01:18,840 --> 00:01:21,359
I'll be taking my sister back to Yan soon.

8
00:01:22,120 --> 00:01:23,400
On your way back to the capital,

9
00:01:23,560 --> 00:01:24,920
take good care of yourselves.

10
00:01:25,079 --> 00:01:26,719
Why didn't Ouyang Yan come for breakfast?

11
00:01:27,040 --> 00:01:27,840
No idea.

12
00:01:29,400 --> 00:01:31,560
I knocked on her door earlier, no answer.

13
00:01:31,799 --> 00:01:32,640
Forget about her.

14
00:01:32,799 --> 00:01:33,599
Let's eat.

15
00:01:35,159 --> 00:01:35,840
I'm full.

16
00:01:35,840 --> 00:01:36,159
Enjoy your meal.

17
00:01:37,319 --> 00:01:37,799
Hey, Qi Zhi.

18
00:01:59,840 --> 00:02:01,120
Why aren't you eating breakfast?

19
00:02:03,680 --> 00:02:04,480
I don't feel like it.

20
00:02:07,120 --> 00:02:08,520
Have you thought about the future?

21
00:02:08,680 --> 00:02:09,479
Hmm?

22
00:02:11,039 --> 00:02:11,919
What future?

23
00:02:14,199 --> 00:02:15,520
We could go to a small town.

24
00:02:15,560 --> 00:02:16,199
You open a martial arts school.

25
00:02:16,199 --> 00:02:16,960
I'll open a small academy.

26
00:02:16,960 --> 00:02:18,120
And teach students together.

27
00:02:21,919 --> 00:02:22,800
Stop joking.

28
00:02:23,759 --> 00:02:24,960
I'm leaving soon.

29
00:02:25,479 --> 00:02:26,599
Imperial Uncle Liu is taking the throne.

30
00:02:26,599 --> 00:02:27,919
You don't need to marry for an alliance.

31
00:02:28,080 --> 00:02:30,319
Are you really going to marry a stranger?

32
00:02:30,439 --> 00:02:31,960
Of course I don't want to.

33
00:02:31,960 --> 00:02:32,159
But...

34
00:02:35,120 --> 00:02:36,879
But I'm still a princess of Yan.

35
00:02:37,879 --> 00:02:38,680
Besides,

36
00:02:39,680 --> 00:02:41,719
my father is still bedridden.

37
00:02:43,039 --> 00:02:44,280
I have to go back sooner or later.

38
00:02:48,439 --> 00:02:50,039
So you really won't go with me?

39
00:02:50,039 --> 00:02:51,199
I want to.

40
00:02:54,680 --> 00:02:55,639
But I can't.

41
00:03:00,120 --> 00:03:01,319
Then I'll have to go with you.

42
00:03:02,599 --> 00:03:03,000
Let's go.

43
00:03:03,120 --> 00:03:03,919
Hey.

44
00:03:04,120 --> 00:03:04,919
Where are we going?

45
00:03:05,439 --> 00:03:06,719
To find the Crown Prince
and Imperial Uncle Liu.

46
00:03:06,719 --> 00:03:07,840
I'm going to ask the two of them

47
00:03:07,840 --> 00:03:08,759
to grant us a marriage.

48
00:03:11,400 --> 00:03:11,800
A-a-a marriage?

49
00:03:17,759 --> 00:03:18,879
I want to marry you.

50
00:03:22,039 --> 00:03:22,439
I...

51
00:03:26,680 --> 00:03:28,479
I thought you'd never...

52
00:03:28,639 --> 00:03:29,039
I accept.

53
00:03:30,560 --> 00:03:31,759
Hahaha!

54
00:03:32,080 --> 00:03:32,879
Chicken farmer!

55
00:03:33,120 --> 00:03:34,840
You finally said what you truly feel!

56
00:03:35,240 --> 00:03:36,800
Hmph, my dear Qi Zhi.

57
00:03:37,080 --> 00:03:37,879
Hehehe.

58
00:03:38,680 --> 00:03:40,479
I knew this day would come for you two!

59
00:03:40,719 --> 00:03:41,520
Hehehe.

60
00:03:42,159 --> 00:03:43,120
Lord Envoy.

61
00:03:44,479 --> 00:03:45,960
I'm leaving my sister in your hands.

62
00:03:45,960 --> 00:03:46,240
Oh my.

63
00:03:46,240 --> 00:03:46,759
Brother!

64
00:03:47,439 --> 00:03:48,719
You were testing me all along!

65
00:03:48,719 --> 00:03:49,280
All right.

66
00:03:49,280 --> 00:03:49,879
Hahaha!

67
00:03:49,919 --> 00:03:51,159
This is a big deal,

68
00:03:51,439 --> 00:03:53,240
let's go inside and discuss it.

69
00:03:53,240 --> 00:03:53,520
No.

70
00:03:53,560 --> 00:03:54,159
Let's go.

71
00:03:54,159 --> 00:03:54,319
You guys...

72
00:03:54,680 --> 00:03:54,960
You're just...

73
00:03:55,719 --> 00:03:56,639
You're just testing me, you...

74
00:03:56,960 --> 00:03:57,960
Come on, let's go.

75
00:03:57,960 --> 00:03:58,360
Hey!

76
00:03:58,560 --> 00:04:00,319
Let's go, Yan'er.

77
00:04:16,720 --> 00:04:17,519
Ah.

78
00:04:18,199 --> 00:04:19,000
You,

79
00:04:19,000 --> 00:04:20,399
don't be too sad.

80
00:04:20,639 --> 00:04:22,319
That chicken farmer is such a blockhead.

81
00:04:22,600 --> 00:04:24,079
He'll never understand you.

82
00:04:26,839 --> 00:04:27,240
Ah.

83
00:04:28,160 --> 00:04:28,839
I really thought

84
00:04:28,839 --> 00:04:31,079
I'd be the heroine of this novel.

85
00:04:34,279 --> 00:04:35,079
Think about it.

86
00:04:35,360 --> 00:04:36,439
Usually in comics,

87
00:04:36,519 --> 00:04:37,959
if the main leads end up together,

88
00:04:38,600 --> 00:04:40,079
then the remaining ones will...

89
00:04:41,480 --> 00:04:43,399
the remaining two will end up together.

90
00:04:44,000 --> 00:04:44,800
Right.

91
00:05:01,519 --> 00:05:02,360
After all these years,

92
00:05:02,759 --> 00:05:04,240
this place hasn't changed a bit.

93
00:05:05,000 --> 00:05:05,800
Imperial Uncle.

94
00:05:06,240 --> 00:05:07,800
Though you never returned to the palace,

95
00:05:08,160 --> 00:05:09,040
my royal father

96
00:05:09,399 --> 00:05:11,079
kept a chamber reserved for you.

97
00:05:14,279 --> 00:05:14,600
Yue'er.

98
00:05:15,639 --> 00:05:18,600
I'll visit Fourth Brother's tomb first.

99
00:05:19,879 --> 00:05:20,680
All right.

100
00:05:31,879 --> 00:05:32,759
Your Highness, Crown Prince.

101
00:05:32,839 --> 00:05:33,839
Your Highness.

102
00:05:33,959 --> 00:05:34,639
You're

103
00:05:34,639 --> 00:05:35,759
finally back.

104
00:05:36,399 --> 00:05:37,199
Teacher.

105
00:05:37,560 --> 00:05:38,319
Imperial Uncle

106
00:05:38,319 --> 00:05:39,759
is no longer just a prince.

107
00:05:40,040 --> 00:05:41,240
He's agreed to take the throne.

108
00:05:41,439 --> 00:05:43,480
He's now the Emperor of Daliang!

109
00:05:44,560 --> 00:05:44,959
Ha!

110
00:05:45,920 --> 00:05:47,279
Congratulations, Your Highness.

111
00:05:47,279 --> 00:05:48,680
Congratulations, Your Highness.

112
00:05:49,279 --> 00:05:50,480
Teacher, there's no need for formalities.

113
00:05:50,959 --> 00:05:51,800
Your Highness,

114
00:05:51,959 --> 00:05:52,920
three days from now

115
00:05:53,000 --> 00:05:54,360
will be an auspicious day.

116
00:05:54,399 --> 00:05:56,160
If the succession is settled,

117
00:05:57,120 --> 00:05:58,959
let's hold the coronation soon

118
00:05:58,959 --> 00:06:00,879
to avoid any complications.

119
00:06:02,000 --> 00:06:02,800
Teacher,

120
00:06:03,480 --> 00:06:05,560
you must pick another auspicious day too.

121
00:06:05,920 --> 00:06:06,879
Uh...

122
00:06:07,959 --> 00:06:09,560
For their wedding day!

123
00:06:13,959 --> 00:06:16,120
Ah, of course, of course.

124
00:06:17,120 --> 00:06:18,000
Your Highness,

125
00:06:18,040 --> 00:06:19,160
as per your instructions,

126
00:06:19,319 --> 00:06:21,839
I've arranged lodgings for everyone.

127
00:06:21,839 --> 00:06:24,040
Please take some rest.

128
00:06:25,800 --> 00:06:26,279
Zhenzhi.

129
00:06:26,279 --> 00:06:26,920
Zhenzhen.

130
00:06:27,079 --> 00:06:27,879
Hey, Crown Prince.

131
00:06:29,279 --> 00:06:29,560
These here

132
00:06:30,319 --> 00:06:32,439
are Daliang's ten most famous novels.

133
00:06:32,600 --> 00:06:33,879
I tracked them all down for you.

134
00:06:34,720 --> 00:06:35,519
Take a look.

135
00:06:36,279 --> 00:06:36,920
And you,

136
00:06:36,920 --> 00:06:37,759
don't rush.

137
00:06:37,759 --> 00:06:38,560
Take your time reading.

138
00:06:38,839 --> 00:06:40,519
Tell me if you need anything.

139
00:06:41,480 --> 00:06:43,839
Don't get bored and leave suddenly, okay?

140
00:06:44,480 --> 00:06:46,720
I bought a lot of your comics today.

141
00:06:46,720 --> 00:06:48,839
But I still love "Young Hero Leaps" most.

142
00:06:48,839 --> 00:06:50,199
Why did you stop drawing it?

143
00:06:52,600 --> 00:06:53,879
"Young Hero Leaps"...

144
00:06:54,279 --> 00:06:54,680
Hmm.

145
00:06:55,000 --> 00:06:57,040
Wasn't I drawing along

146
00:06:57,279 --> 00:06:59,000
when I went to find the chicken farmer?

147
00:06:59,240 --> 00:06:59,959
And after that,

148
00:06:59,959 --> 00:07:01,120
I was always on the road.

149
00:07:01,160 --> 00:07:02,600
I didn't have time to think about it.

150
00:07:02,920 --> 00:07:03,600
Then from now on,

151
00:07:03,600 --> 00:07:04,879
I'll help you come up with ideas.

152
00:07:05,120 --> 00:07:06,079
I'll write the novel,

153
00:07:06,079 --> 00:07:06,959
you draw the comics.

154
00:07:08,319 --> 00:07:08,639
Really?

155
00:07:08,839 --> 00:07:09,240
Mm.

156
00:07:09,480 --> 00:07:10,839
I plan to stay.

157
00:07:12,000 --> 00:07:13,000
That's wonderful, Zhenzhen!

158
00:07:14,519 --> 00:07:14,800
I know.

159
00:07:15,600 --> 00:07:16,399
You've always loved

160
00:07:17,040 --> 00:07:18,079
wandering around outside.

161
00:07:18,920 --> 00:07:19,480
You're willing to stay,

162
00:07:20,439 --> 00:07:21,120
it must be because of me.

163
00:07:21,600 --> 00:07:22,279
Right.

164
00:07:22,279 --> 00:07:23,920
It's for the candied hawthorns here.

165
00:07:23,920 --> 00:07:25,240
They're just way too delicious!

166
00:07:29,160 --> 00:07:29,959
Zhenzhen.

167
00:07:30,480 --> 00:07:31,600
Well, if you find them tasty,

168
00:07:32,120 --> 00:07:33,279
then have some more.

169
00:07:33,319 --> 00:07:34,120
Mm.

170
00:07:38,800 --> 00:07:39,600
Princess,

171
00:07:39,839 --> 00:07:40,879
this mandarin-duck wedding gown

172
00:07:40,879 --> 00:07:42,839
is the most beautiful one we have.

173
00:07:44,720 --> 00:07:45,519
I don't want it.

174
00:07:47,120 --> 00:07:47,519
Princess,

175
00:07:48,000 --> 00:07:49,480
what exactly do you want?

176
00:07:50,040 --> 00:07:51,639
Prepare casual clothes for the princess.

177
00:07:54,079 --> 00:07:54,879
Casual clothes?

178
00:07:55,519 --> 00:07:56,879
Getting married in casual wear?

179
00:07:57,759 --> 00:07:59,240
This...

180
00:07:59,240 --> 00:08:00,160
Since ancient times,

181
00:08:00,199 --> 00:08:01,879
there's never been such a thing.

182
00:08:02,600 --> 00:08:04,360
Just go along with the princess.

183
00:08:04,480 --> 00:08:05,920
If she gets angry,

184
00:08:05,920 --> 00:08:07,680
she'll beat us both up.

185
00:08:08,680 --> 00:08:09,439
Yes.

186
00:08:09,439 --> 00:08:11,040
I will go prepare them now.

187
00:08:13,000 --> 00:08:13,399
Hey!

188
00:08:15,319 --> 00:08:17,399
When have I ever been like that?

189
00:08:18,600 --> 00:08:19,399
Fine, fine, fine.

190
00:08:19,439 --> 00:08:20,639
You'll only beat me up, okay?

191
00:08:20,680 --> 00:08:21,800
Only me.

192
00:08:24,959 --> 00:08:26,040
Hold out your hand.

193
00:08:34,200 --> 00:08:35,919
What is this?

194
00:08:36,559 --> 00:08:37,799
This is way too ugly.

195
00:08:37,840 --> 00:08:38,639
Where'd you get it?

196
00:08:39,440 --> 00:08:40,320
I had it made.

197
00:08:45,480 --> 00:08:45,879
Uh...

198
00:08:47,879 --> 00:08:48,840
You know...

199
00:08:50,360 --> 00:08:51,559
No wonder it's so ugly.

200
00:08:54,559 --> 00:08:55,799
If it's ugly, give it back.

201
00:08:56,399 --> 00:08:57,360
No way.

202
00:08:57,679 --> 00:08:58,679
You already gave it to me.

203
00:08:58,720 --> 00:08:59,600
So it's mine now.

204
00:09:02,519 --> 00:09:03,320
Come with me.

205
00:09:03,480 --> 00:09:04,279
Where to?

206
00:09:04,600 --> 00:09:05,279
Boss.

207
00:09:05,279 --> 00:09:06,759
Blue dragon on left, white tiger on right,

208
00:09:06,759 --> 00:09:08,240
and a Mickey Mouse in the middle?

209
00:09:08,240 --> 00:09:08,960
Hehehe.

210
00:09:09,240 --> 00:09:10,679
The styles don't match.

211
00:09:11,440 --> 00:09:12,399
What the hell do you know?

212
00:09:12,919 --> 00:09:14,000
This is swagger.

213
00:09:14,679 --> 00:09:15,399
Besides,

214
00:09:15,399 --> 00:09:16,480
your sister-in-law likes it.

215
00:09:16,679 --> 00:09:17,480
Oh my.

216
00:09:17,960 --> 00:09:19,360
A couple, huh?

217
00:09:19,840 --> 00:09:21,279
We have a couples package.

218
00:09:21,279 --> 00:09:22,279
"Forever and Always,"

219
00:09:22,279 --> 00:09:23,360
"Happily Ever After,"

220
00:09:23,440 --> 00:09:24,240
eight characters total.

221
00:09:24,320 --> 00:09:26,120
Comes with a free heart design.

222
00:09:26,159 --> 00:09:26,960
How about it?

223
00:09:27,159 --> 00:09:27,960
Ah.

224
00:09:28,759 --> 00:09:29,519
No thanks, boss.

225
00:09:29,519 --> 00:09:30,200
I want

226
00:09:30,200 --> 00:09:31,519
a wedding ring tattooed on my hand.

227
00:09:31,639 --> 00:09:32,360
This...

228
00:09:33,000 --> 00:09:33,799
A wedding ring?

229
00:09:34,919 --> 00:09:36,600
That's not really a good idea.

230
00:09:36,639 --> 00:09:37,440
Oh.

231
00:09:37,720 --> 00:09:40,120
What I mean is, rings...

232
00:09:40,240 --> 00:09:41,360
they always end up getting lost.

233
00:09:42,039 --> 00:09:42,840
But

234
00:09:42,919 --> 00:09:44,639
if it's on your body, you can't lose it.

235
00:09:44,639 --> 00:09:45,279
Oh.

236
00:09:47,600 --> 00:09:48,840
You just love talking nonsense.

237
00:09:54,200 --> 00:09:56,360
Did you just peek at me?

238
00:09:57,639 --> 00:09:59,200
Peek at what I was thinking?

239
00:10:00,080 --> 00:10:00,879
No.

240
00:10:01,519 --> 00:10:03,000
With others, I'd need to peek,

241
00:10:03,159 --> 00:10:04,240
but not with you.

242
00:10:14,240 --> 00:10:16,200
I know your biggest fear is loss.

243
00:10:18,240 --> 00:10:20,200
You've already lost your princess title,

244
00:10:21,080 --> 00:10:22,360
you've lost the Great Yan Kingdom.

245
00:10:24,960 --> 00:10:26,840
Now, by tattooing the ring on my body,

246
00:10:27,120 --> 00:10:28,600
I just want to tell you

247
00:10:30,759 --> 00:10:32,000
that you can never lose me.

248
00:10:48,360 --> 00:10:49,159
Imperial Uncle.

249
00:10:49,600 --> 00:10:50,399
After you.

250
00:10:51,720 --> 00:10:52,639
Please.

251
00:11:03,200 --> 00:11:04,000
Fourth Brother.

252
00:11:05,399 --> 00:11:06,200
Back in the day,

253
00:11:07,039 --> 00:11:09,200
the two of us fought over this chair,

254
00:11:09,919 --> 00:11:11,480
fought tooth and nail.

255
00:11:13,240 --> 00:11:14,240
And in the blink of an eye,

256
00:11:15,519 --> 00:11:17,000
over 20 years have passed.

257
00:11:17,879 --> 00:11:20,200
Now, having me sit on this dragon throne,

258
00:11:21,919 --> 00:11:22,799
Heh.

259
00:11:22,879 --> 00:11:23,840
my heart

260
00:11:24,639 --> 00:11:26,440
feels so bittersweet.

261
00:11:28,000 --> 00:11:28,799
Imperial Uncle,

262
00:11:29,480 --> 00:11:30,840
don't be too sorrowful.

263
00:11:31,519 --> 00:11:33,440
If Father knew in the afterlife,

264
00:11:33,759 --> 00:11:35,000
he'd surely be pleased.

265
00:11:35,759 --> 00:11:36,600
Quit being sentimental.

266
00:11:36,600 --> 00:11:37,720
Let's get started.

267
00:11:38,879 --> 00:11:39,519
Mm.

268
00:11:39,960 --> 00:11:40,879
Alright.

269
00:11:41,480 --> 00:11:42,720
Begin the rehearsal.

270
00:11:49,000 --> 00:11:50,200
Ouyang Que!

271
00:11:50,279 --> 00:11:51,080
What are you doing?

272
00:11:51,120 --> 00:11:52,320
Crown Prince,

273
00:11:53,120 --> 00:11:55,639
I rid you of Daliang's worst traitor.

274
00:11:56,320 --> 00:11:58,440
Shouldn't I be the Emperor?

275
00:11:58,679 --> 00:11:58,960
Ouyang Que!

276
00:12:00,879 --> 00:12:02,399
Is that throne yours to sit on?

277
00:12:03,639 --> 00:12:04,759
Get down now!

278
00:12:05,240 --> 00:12:06,039
Guards!

279
00:12:11,399 --> 00:12:13,279
Seize this traitor!

280
00:12:15,759 --> 00:12:16,840
What are you doing?

281
00:12:17,159 --> 00:12:18,000
Are you all rebelling?

282
00:12:21,480 --> 00:12:23,519
Since I dare to stand here today,

283
00:12:24,559 --> 00:12:26,320
it means I'm fully prepared.

284
00:12:27,120 --> 00:12:29,559
The palace troops have all pledged to me.

285
00:12:30,039 --> 00:12:31,679
As long as you submit to me,

286
00:12:32,159 --> 00:12:34,679
you can still enjoy glory and wealth.

287
00:12:34,679 --> 00:12:36,200
You mean wealth and glory, right?

288
00:12:36,240 --> 00:12:37,240
In your dreams.

289
00:12:57,600 --> 00:12:58,480
Take them all

290
00:12:59,759 --> 00:13:00,559
away.

291
00:13:02,440 --> 00:13:02,840
Brother.

292
00:13:03,200 --> 00:13:04,000
Take them away.

293
00:13:24,480 --> 00:13:25,279
Who goes there?

294
00:13:25,480 --> 00:13:26,919
Just delivering some food.

295
00:13:45,320 --> 00:13:46,120
Your Highness.

296
00:13:46,200 --> 00:13:47,679
I've brought you some food.

297
00:13:48,559 --> 00:13:49,480
Little Huzi.

298
00:13:55,919 --> 00:13:57,000
Thank you, Little Huzi.

299
00:13:57,240 --> 00:13:58,039
Little Huzi.

300
00:13:58,360 --> 00:13:59,399
Do you know how the Grand Scholar

301
00:13:59,399 --> 00:14:01,399
ended up scheming with Ouyang Que?

302
00:14:01,639 --> 00:14:02,039
Well...

303
00:14:03,159 --> 00:14:04,360
I'm not really sure.

304
00:14:04,720 --> 00:14:05,120
Oh.

305
00:14:07,320 --> 00:14:09,759
But his servant Little Yingzi told me

306
00:14:10,039 --> 00:14:12,639
the Grand Scholar murdered General Li.

307
00:14:13,000 --> 00:14:13,799
What?

308
00:14:14,879 --> 00:14:16,279
General Li is dead?

309
00:14:16,759 --> 00:14:17,559
Impossible.

310
00:14:17,960 --> 00:14:19,039
That can't possibly be true.

311
00:14:19,080 --> 00:14:19,879
It's true.

312
00:14:20,360 --> 00:14:21,600
And I also heard

313
00:14:21,799 --> 00:14:23,000
that at the Grand Scholar's residence,

314
00:14:23,120 --> 00:14:24,639
there's a letter left by General Li.

315
00:14:24,799 --> 00:14:25,919
I'll go steal it later.

316
00:14:25,919 --> 00:14:27,080
One look and you'll understand.

317
00:14:27,240 --> 00:14:28,039
Good.

318
00:14:28,240 --> 00:14:29,200
Then hurry there and back.

319
00:14:29,200 --> 00:14:29,840
Okay.

320
00:14:35,600 --> 00:14:36,519
Be careful.

321
00:14:36,519 --> 00:14:37,200
Hey!

322
00:14:38,600 --> 00:14:39,840
If you don't let me out,

323
00:14:39,879 --> 00:14:42,600
I'll beat every one of you to death!

324
00:14:46,120 --> 00:14:47,480
I swear I'll burn this place down!

325
00:14:49,960 --> 00:14:52,559
Ouyang Que, what are you really after?

326
00:14:53,679 --> 00:14:57,279
Didn't Imperial Uncle Liu agree to
help us attack Watanabe?

327
00:14:57,279 --> 00:14:58,480
Yan'er, do you remember?

328
00:14:59,639 --> 00:15:01,279
The year the Crown Prince was born,

329
00:15:01,559 --> 00:15:02,639
I was seven,

330
00:15:03,320 --> 00:15:04,320
and you were two.

331
00:15:05,279 --> 00:15:07,440
Father brought us to Daliang to celebrate.

332
00:15:08,440 --> 00:15:10,200
We stayed in this very room.

333
00:15:11,279 --> 00:15:12,559
I was only two.

334
00:15:12,600 --> 00:15:13,799
What could I possibly remember?

335
00:15:17,080 --> 00:15:19,679
Yan was already in decline back then.

336
00:15:20,080 --> 00:15:23,639
Even the room attendants looked down on us.

337
00:15:25,240 --> 00:15:27,399
They gave us drafty, broken-down rooms.

338
00:15:28,120 --> 00:15:29,480
You're overthinking it.

339
00:15:29,960 --> 00:15:32,080
The rooms here all look the same to me.

340
00:15:33,879 --> 00:15:35,559
Father later caught a chill,

341
00:15:35,679 --> 00:15:36,960
and couldn't attend the ceremony.

342
00:15:39,279 --> 00:15:40,039
That day,

343
00:15:41,919 --> 00:15:44,840
the palace was full of laughter and joy.

344
00:15:46,039 --> 00:15:47,159
But us?

345
00:15:50,279 --> 00:15:52,200
They didn't even bring us a single meal.

346
00:16:03,960 --> 00:16:05,039
From that day on,

347
00:16:05,679 --> 00:16:06,879
I understood.

348
00:16:08,679 --> 00:16:10,240
I must seize this throne.

349
00:16:12,559 --> 00:16:15,000
I'll make this whole world belong to Yan.

350
00:16:15,759 --> 00:16:16,480
But...

351
00:16:17,399 --> 00:16:20,759
Watanabe's forces are at Yan's gates.

352
00:16:21,519 --> 00:16:24,240
You're fighting for a throne
instead of leading our troops?

353
00:16:24,679 --> 00:16:25,600
What about our people?

354
00:16:25,600 --> 00:16:26,879
Once I have the throne,

355
00:16:27,120 --> 00:16:28,919
everyone in the world will be my people.

356
00:16:28,919 --> 00:16:30,120
You only care about yourself.

357
00:16:35,960 --> 00:16:36,919
You've changed.

358
00:16:40,679 --> 00:16:42,240
My brother was never like this.

359
00:16:46,320 --> 00:16:47,639
Yan'er, do you know

360
00:16:49,000 --> 00:16:51,799
who is most trustworthy in this world?

361
00:16:54,600 --> 00:16:55,799
Not family,

362
00:16:57,120 --> 00:16:58,080
and certainly not friends.

363
00:17:03,120 --> 00:17:04,839
It's a dead enemy.

364
00:17:17,240 --> 00:17:17,640
Crown Prince.

365
00:17:17,960 --> 00:17:19,200
At least eat something.

366
00:17:19,200 --> 00:17:20,839
Otherwise, before Teacher rescues us,

367
00:17:21,279 --> 00:17:22,759
you'll have starved to death in this cell.

368
00:17:24,440 --> 00:17:25,759
You still call him Teacher?

369
00:17:26,680 --> 00:17:28,160
You still trust him now, do you?

370
00:17:29,079 --> 00:17:31,440
But at this point, who else can we trust?

371
00:17:38,839 --> 00:17:39,799
Our only option now

372
00:17:40,000 --> 00:17:41,440
is for you to agree to abdicate first.

373
00:17:41,519 --> 00:17:42,759
Once we're out of this cell,

374
00:17:42,759 --> 00:17:44,119
things will have a chance to turn around.

375
00:17:45,680 --> 00:17:46,720
How can you guarantee

376
00:17:47,000 --> 00:17:48,799
that things will turn around if I abdicate?

377
00:17:49,599 --> 00:17:51,480
What if Ouyang Que really becomes emperor?

378
00:17:51,720 --> 00:17:53,119
What about the people of Daliang then?

379
00:17:53,640 --> 00:17:55,359
I can't guarantee a turnaround,

380
00:17:55,359 --> 00:17:57,160
but only by first gaining his trust

381
00:17:57,160 --> 00:17:59,359
will we have a chance to strike at him.

382
00:18:00,200 --> 00:18:01,079
You two

383
00:18:01,279 --> 00:18:03,759
keep telling me to
gain Ouyang Que's trust.

384
00:18:04,599 --> 00:18:05,400
Who knows

385
00:18:05,559 --> 00:18:07,200
if you two aren't conspiring together

386
00:18:07,519 --> 00:18:08,440
to trick me into abdicating?

387
00:18:12,039 --> 00:18:13,599
Is that how you see me?

388
00:18:18,319 --> 00:18:19,119
Qi Zhi.

389
00:18:21,880 --> 00:18:22,680
Crown Prince.

390
00:18:22,680 --> 00:18:23,440
Zhenzhen.

391
00:18:24,240 --> 00:18:25,079
My mind is made up.

392
00:18:25,759 --> 00:18:26,920
There's no need to say more.

393
00:18:28,640 --> 00:18:30,559
I don't get what Qi Zhi said either.

394
00:18:30,759 --> 00:18:32,200
I don't understand affairs of state,

395
00:18:32,279 --> 00:18:33,640
nor power struggles for the throne.

396
00:18:34,039 --> 00:18:35,519
I just hope we can get out safely.

397
00:18:35,519 --> 00:18:36,599
Zhenzhen, don't say any more.

398
00:18:37,359 --> 00:18:39,599
We agreed you'd draw and I'd write, right?

399
00:18:39,599 --> 00:18:40,359
Enough!

400
00:18:43,240 --> 00:18:44,039
I'm sorry.

401
00:18:45,240 --> 00:18:46,240
Had I known this would happen,

402
00:18:46,279 --> 00:18:47,440
why would I have stayed?

403
00:18:47,440 --> 00:18:48,160
Hmph.

404
00:18:50,039 --> 00:18:52,039
You just want Daliang's throne, don't you?

405
00:18:53,960 --> 00:18:54,759
I'll help you.

406
00:18:56,279 --> 00:18:57,240
I don't need your help.

407
00:18:58,920 --> 00:19:00,200
I can seize it myself.

408
00:19:03,279 --> 00:19:04,599
There are so many princes in Daliang.

409
00:19:05,519 --> 00:19:06,599
You can kill one,

410
00:19:07,839 --> 00:19:09,319
you can kill them all,

411
00:19:12,440 --> 00:19:14,680
can you kill everyone in the realm?

412
00:19:15,119 --> 00:19:16,559
You'd be making countless enemies.

413
00:19:17,200 --> 00:19:19,359
When they try to bring you down later,

414
00:19:20,720 --> 00:19:22,119
avenging the Crown Prince

415
00:19:22,559 --> 00:19:24,519
will be their best pretext.

416
00:19:33,119 --> 00:19:35,359
So Yan'er, do you have a better plan?

417
00:19:35,440 --> 00:19:36,680
I'll marry the Crown Prince.

418
00:19:38,039 --> 00:19:39,240
Once you become the Imperial In-law,

419
00:19:39,880 --> 00:19:41,640
you can naturally rule the court.

420
00:19:43,160 --> 00:19:45,200
Just keep the Crown Prince in check,

421
00:19:46,480 --> 00:19:47,960
and he'll become your puppet.

422
00:19:49,200 --> 00:19:50,160
This way,

423
00:19:50,960 --> 00:19:52,640
you can legitimately

424
00:19:53,200 --> 00:19:54,720
silence all the gossiping tongues.

425
00:19:56,559 --> 00:19:57,160
Only then

426
00:19:58,920 --> 00:19:59,559
will you

427
00:20:00,720 --> 00:20:01,759
sit firmly on this throne.

428
00:20:18,599 --> 00:20:19,400
Your Highness.

429
00:20:20,400 --> 00:20:21,200
Your Highness.

430
00:20:21,400 --> 00:20:22,200
Little Huzi.

431
00:20:26,559 --> 00:20:27,359
Your Highness.

432
00:20:27,440 --> 00:20:28,319
What happened?

433
00:20:29,480 --> 00:20:30,039
The letter.

434
00:20:31,000 --> 00:20:32,200
I stole the letter.

435
00:20:35,240 --> 00:20:36,039
Dear brother,

436
00:20:36,680 --> 00:20:38,880
Watanabe and Liang are now at war.

437
00:20:39,400 --> 00:20:40,960
Because I am a Watanabe princess,

438
00:20:41,359 --> 00:20:43,799
the Empress Dowager had me cast out.

439
00:20:44,440 --> 00:20:45,559
Worn out from the long journey,

440
00:20:45,599 --> 00:20:47,119
and troubled in heart,

441
00:20:47,480 --> 00:20:48,839
I gave birth prematurely on horseback,

442
00:20:49,000 --> 00:20:50,240
delivering a baby boy.

443
00:20:51,039 --> 00:20:53,160
Weak and penniless,

444
00:20:53,599 --> 00:20:55,039
hoping for my son's safety,

445
00:20:55,039 --> 00:20:56,359
I changed his name.

446
00:20:56,559 --> 00:20:58,480
"Qi" from "ordering family and state,"

447
00:20:58,799 --> 00:21:00,440
and "Zhi" from your name, brother,

448
00:21:00,960 --> 00:21:02,279
naming him Qi Zhi.

449
00:21:06,480 --> 00:21:07,279
Qi Zhi.

450
00:21:11,720 --> 00:21:13,839
What a loyal little servant.

451
00:21:16,319 --> 00:21:17,160
Ouyang Que!

452
00:21:20,759 --> 00:21:21,559
Your Highness!

453
00:21:22,039 --> 00:21:22,839
Stop!

454
00:21:24,160 --> 00:21:25,000
What are you doing?

455
00:21:28,480 --> 00:21:29,279
Little Huzi!

456
00:21:33,839 --> 00:21:34,640
Ouyang Que!

457
00:21:35,000 --> 00:21:36,000
Let me out!

458
00:21:36,839 --> 00:21:38,559
Letting you out is fine,

459
00:21:39,400 --> 00:21:42,119
as long as the Crown Prince
marries my sister tomorrow,

460
00:21:43,039 --> 00:21:45,079
then naturally I'll let you all go.

461
00:21:46,400 --> 00:21:47,240
What did you say?

462
00:21:49,119 --> 00:21:50,000
Qi Zhi,

463
00:21:50,559 --> 00:21:52,640
you really should thank my sister.

464
00:21:53,400 --> 00:21:56,240
She volunteered to marry the Crown Prince

465
00:21:56,480 --> 00:21:58,279
just to spare your worthless little life.

466
00:22:29,680 --> 00:22:30,480
Hm?

467
00:22:32,079 --> 00:22:32,880
What?

468
00:22:33,559 --> 00:22:34,759
Now you won't even let me in?

469
00:22:35,880 --> 00:22:37,440
If the Crown Prince starves,

470
00:22:37,839 --> 00:22:38,279
the prince

471
00:22:38,279 --> 00:22:40,160
will not forgive you.

472
00:22:40,599 --> 00:22:41,400
Move aside.

473
00:22:54,920 --> 00:22:55,720
Teacher.

474
00:22:57,039 --> 00:22:57,720
Don't say a word.

475
00:22:57,720 --> 00:22:58,839
Change your clothes and come with me.

476
00:22:58,839 --> 00:22:59,240
Quickly!

477
00:22:59,240 --> 00:23:00,240
What about the two of them?

478
00:23:01,160 --> 00:23:02,599
I'll find another way to save them.

479
00:23:02,599 --> 00:23:03,319
No, no.

480
00:23:03,319 --> 00:23:04,720
I can't leave the Crown Prince alone.

481
00:23:05,359 --> 00:23:06,680
I can only take one person now,

482
00:23:06,680 --> 00:23:09,039
or the guards will get suspicious.

483
00:23:10,720 --> 00:23:11,519
Teacher,

484
00:23:11,519 --> 00:23:13,559
I'm a lowly palace chicken farmer.

485
00:23:13,599 --> 00:23:14,440
If I die, I die.

486
00:23:14,440 --> 00:23:15,799
If you can really only take one,

487
00:23:15,799 --> 00:23:16,559
take the Crown Prince.

488
00:23:16,559 --> 00:23:17,480
Take the Crown Prince.

489
00:23:19,119 --> 00:23:21,559
The palace knows the Crown Prince's face.

490
00:23:21,640 --> 00:23:22,359
Besides,

491
00:23:22,359 --> 00:23:23,440
the method to rescue you

492
00:23:23,440 --> 00:23:25,799
can't save the Crown Prince, you know it.

493
00:23:26,119 --> 00:23:27,240
Only if you get out first

494
00:23:27,240 --> 00:23:29,559
can we plan to come back for them.

495
00:23:30,319 --> 00:23:31,119
Qi Zhi,

496
00:23:31,799 --> 00:23:32,599
do you really

497
00:23:33,119 --> 00:23:35,359
want to see Ouyang Yan marry another?

498
00:23:36,559 --> 00:23:37,359
Hurry!

499
00:23:41,400 --> 00:23:42,200
Qi Zhi,

500
00:23:42,880 --> 00:23:43,720
get in the carriage.

501
00:23:43,720 --> 00:23:45,279
Leave the city, run as far as you can.

502
00:23:45,440 --> 00:23:46,240
Leave the city?

503
00:23:47,200 --> 00:23:48,880
How do I save the Crown Prince
and Zhen Fei from outside?

504
00:23:48,880 --> 00:23:50,000
Ouyang Yan is still in the palace!

505
00:23:50,000 --> 00:23:51,759
Right now, keeping you safe matters most.

506
00:23:51,759 --> 00:23:52,240
As for them,

507
00:23:52,240 --> 00:23:53,480
I'll find a chance to rescue them.

508
00:23:55,279 --> 00:23:56,759
You tricked me into leaving, didn't you?

509
00:23:58,599 --> 00:24:00,000
It was the only way.

510
00:24:00,279 --> 00:24:02,519
You know how hard it was to get you out.

511
00:24:03,039 --> 00:24:03,839
Qi Zhi,

512
00:24:04,319 --> 00:24:05,160
promise me

513
00:24:05,960 --> 00:24:07,000
you'll stay alive.

514
00:24:08,599 --> 00:24:09,400
Get in the carriage.

515
00:24:11,920 --> 00:24:12,720
Alright.

516
00:24:16,599 --> 00:24:17,079
You...

517
00:24:17,079 --> 00:24:18,160
If Ouyang Yan dies,

518
00:24:18,160 --> 00:24:19,279
I won't live on alone.

519
00:24:29,319 --> 00:24:30,519
Where did Qi Zhi go?

520
00:24:32,519 --> 00:24:33,880
It seems the Grand Scholar

521
00:24:33,880 --> 00:24:34,920
just rescued him.

522
00:24:35,839 --> 00:24:36,680
What did you say?

523
00:24:40,359 --> 00:24:41,160
Qi Zhi.

524
00:24:41,720 --> 00:24:42,799
Why are you here?

525
00:24:43,079 --> 00:24:44,240
I came to save you. Come with me.

526
00:24:45,720 --> 00:24:46,519
I can't leave.

527
00:24:48,240 --> 00:24:49,039
Why?

528
00:24:49,799 --> 00:24:50,640
I can't leave.

529
00:24:51,519 --> 00:24:52,240
If I go,

530
00:24:52,240 --> 00:24:53,200
everyone will die.

531
00:24:53,359 --> 00:24:54,920
I'll save the others. Come with me.

532
00:24:54,920 --> 00:24:56,359
Don't you understand yet?

533
00:24:56,599 --> 00:24:57,920
Only I can save them all.

534
00:24:59,519 --> 00:25:00,759
When I first came to Daliang,

535
00:25:00,759 --> 00:25:02,279
I was betrothed to the Crown Prince.

536
00:25:02,480 --> 00:25:03,279
Now,

537
00:25:04,799 --> 00:25:06,880
I've finally gotten what I wanted.

538
00:25:09,400 --> 00:25:10,319
You should leave now.

539
00:25:11,359 --> 00:25:12,519
And never come back.

540
00:25:14,079 --> 00:25:15,759
We already have the rings tattooed on us.

541
00:25:16,200 --> 00:25:17,720
How can you just ignore me?

542
00:25:42,200 --> 00:25:43,000
I don't care.

543
00:25:43,160 --> 00:25:43,960
Let's go.

544
00:25:46,559 --> 00:25:47,359
Guards!

545
00:25:47,640 --> 00:25:48,559
Seize the traitor!

546
00:25:49,759 --> 00:25:50,559
Ouyang Yan!

547
00:25:50,640 --> 00:25:51,200
Go!

548
00:25:51,200 --> 00:25:52,039
Ouyang Yan!

549
00:26:00,640 --> 00:26:01,440
Qi Zhi.

550
00:26:05,000 --> 00:26:05,839
I'm sorry.

551
00:26:15,440 --> 00:26:16,960
Qi Zhi!

552
00:26:20,599 --> 00:26:21,400
Qi Zhi!

553
00:26:23,079 --> 00:26:24,200
Your Highness.

554
00:26:24,680 --> 00:26:25,480
After you.

555
00:26:26,720 --> 00:26:28,119
Just give up.

556
00:26:29,279 --> 00:26:30,559
I'm not going with you.

557
00:26:32,480 --> 00:26:34,160
A wedding is a joyous occasion.

558
00:26:34,759 --> 00:26:36,039
Why the long face?

559
00:26:36,039 --> 00:26:37,039
Just kill me.

560
00:26:41,799 --> 00:26:44,519
Your Highness, how do you want me to beg?

561
00:26:46,000 --> 00:26:47,759
You think I don't dare kill you?

562
00:26:51,559 --> 00:26:52,359
Crown Prince.

563
00:26:56,240 --> 00:26:57,680
I hear if you take the throne now,

564
00:26:58,000 --> 00:27:00,599
you can marry the beautiful Yan Princess.

565
00:27:06,960 --> 00:27:07,920
Don't forget,

566
00:27:08,440 --> 00:27:10,640
the one rightfully entitled to the throne

567
00:27:11,319 --> 00:27:12,400
isn't only the Crown Prince,

568
00:27:13,039 --> 00:27:14,319
but also me, Liu Heng.
